## <a id="troubleshooting"></a> Installation Troubleshooting

If `bosh_cli` gem installation does not succeed, make sure pre-requisites for your OS are met.

### Prerequisites on Ubuntu Trusty

Make sure following packages are installed:

<pre class="terminal">
sudo apt-get install build-essential ruby ruby-dev libxml2-dev libsqlite3-dev libxslt1-dev libpq-dev libmysqlclient-dev
</pre>

